    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Schizophrenia</strong> is a psychological survival horror. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don't remember anything. You have to survive in the bunker in order to get out of it. Look for and use all the items that come your way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The bunker can be dangerous. Who knows who might even be there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/3d31e22808353188f7ce50779fcd2db1.avif?t=1772348973\" width=1560 height=296 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/fb88121403cb4c397e1e758d4b0b7a8d.poster.avif?t=1772348973\" width=720 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/fb88121403cb4c397e1e758d4b0b7a8d.webm?t=1772348973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/fb88121403cb4c397e1e758d4b0b7a8d.mp4?t=1772348973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/c9044b5e14d09a58407b2b09aa705205.avif?t=1772348973\" width=1560 height=296 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bunker</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The bunker is equipped with a water supply system and electricity supply. But the lights begin to flicker. The hike will have to refuel the generator. The water stopped flowing. The water supply system may need to be repaired.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/4ff6db95e14777c8e3659ecc0682cd1b.poster.avif?t=1772348973\" width=720 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/4ff6db95e14777c8e3659ecc0682cd1b.webm?t=1772348973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/4ff6db95e14777c8e3659ecc0682cd1b.mp4?t=1772348973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/d9a45bd302ed77bc293ce5246ced7c5b.avif?t=1772348973\" width=1560 height=296 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Growing horror</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While in this bunker you begin to go crazy. You feel like someone is watching you. Strange sounds are constantly heard. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something needs to be done to avoid going crazy. Find the pills.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/335cff5c09ac0870a67e9f341f786fb8.avif?t=1772348973\" width=1560 height=296 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bunker Dwellers</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Could the inhabitants of the bunker be dangerous? What can you generally expect from them? It’s better for me to get around them or better find weapons for protection. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember. The main thing is not to go crazy. And further. Don't make loud noises. They can hear you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/2fa255148823925219e1d0b003fb7d6c.poster.avif?t=1772348973\" width=720 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/2fa255148823925219e1d0b003fb7d6c.webm?t=1772348973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/2fa255148823925219e1d0b003fb7d6c.mp4?t=1772348973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/9d84512a32e30013233739968518e47e.poster.avif?t=1772348973\" width=1170 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/9d84512a32e30013233739968518e47e.webm?t=1772348973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093510/extras/9d84512a32e30013233739968518e47e.mp4?t=1772348973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
